<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="no"><head><title>Kunngjøring om avgifter til statskassen.</title><base href="https://lovdata.no/" /></head><body><header class="documentHeader" id="hode"><dl class="data-document-key-info"><dt class="xmlGenerated">XML generert</dt><dd class="xmlGenerated">2025-11-18 09:19:20</dd><dt class="legacyID">Datokode</dt><dd class="legacyID">FOR-1987-06-12-502</dd><dt class="dokid">DokumentID</dt><dd class="dokid">LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502</dd><dt class="ministry">Departement</dt><dd class="ministry"><ul><li>Finans- og tolldepartementet</li></ul></dd><dt class="publishedIn">Publisert i</dt><dd class="publishedIn">Avd I 1987 Nr. 14</dd><dt class="dateInForce">I kraft fra</dt><dd class="dateInForce">1987-08-03</dd><dt class="appliesTo">Gjelder for</dt><dd class="appliesTo">Norge</dd><dt class="dateOfPublication">Kunngjort</dt><dd class="dateOfPublication">1987-07-03</dd><dt class="title">Tittel</dt><dd class="title">Kunngjøring om avgifter til statskassen.</dd><dt class="miscInformation">Annet om dokumentet</dt><dd class="miscInformation">Kunngjøring fra Finans- og tolldepartementet.</dd><dt class="refid">RefID</dt><dd class="refid">forskrift/1987-06-12-502</dd><dt class="table-of-contents">Innhold</dt><dd class="table-of-contents"><ul class="tocTopUl"><li>Kunngjøring om avgifter til statskassen.<ul class="tocSubUl"><li>I.</li><li>II.</li><li>III.</li><li>IV.<ul class="tocSubUl"><li>§ 1.</li><li>§ 2.</li><li>§ 3.</li><li>§ 4.</li><li>§ 5.</li><li>§ 6.</li><li>§ 7.</li><li>§ 8.</li><li>§ 9.</li><li>§ 10.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></dd></dl></header><main class="documentBody" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502" id="dokument"><h1>Kunngjøring om avgifter til statskassen.</h1><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/1/" id="ledd-1">Stortinget har 12. juni 1987 fattet følgende vedtak:</article><section class="section" data-name="kapI" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/" id="kapittel-1" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/KAPITTEL_1" data-partID="k1"><h2 data-text-align="center">I.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">Fra 1. juli 1987 skal § 1 bokstav b i Stortingets vedtak av 8. desember 1986 nr. 2190 om omregistreringsavgift m.v. lyde:<table><thead><tr><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><th colspan="4" data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">Reg. år/modellår</th></tr><tr><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">1987</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">1983</th></tr><tr><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">og</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">eller</th></tr><tr><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">1986</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">1985</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">1984</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">eldre</th></tr><tr><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top" /><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">kr</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">kr</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">kr</th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">kr</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">b. <i>Personbiler. Busser</i></td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top"> Egenvekt (typegodkjent):</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top" /></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">1. t.o.m. 800 kg.</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">4.390 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">3.360 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">2.520 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">1.680 </td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">2. over 800 t.o.m. 1.200 kg.</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">6.020 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">4.660 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">3.470 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">2.390 </td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">3. over 1.200 t.o.m. 1.600 kg.</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">8.650 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">6.700 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">4.910 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">3.360 </td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">4. over 1.600 kg.</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">11.150 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">8.610 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">6.340 </td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">4.310 </td></tr></tbody></table></article></section><section class="section" data-name="kapII" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/" id="kapittel-2" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/KAPITTEL_2" data-partID="k2"><h2 data-text-align="center">II.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-2-ledd-1">Fra 1. juli 1987 skal avgiftssatsen i § 1, 1. ledd i Stortingets vedtak av 8. desember 1986 om dokumentavgift være 2,5 pst. dog minst fra kr. 100.</article></section><section class="section" data-name="kapIII" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/3/" id="kapittel-3" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/KAPITTEL_3" data-partID="k3"><h2 data-text-align="center">III.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-3-ledd-1">I Stortingets vedtak av 8. desember 1986 om avgift på elektrisk kraft skal § 2, 1. ledd lyde:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/3/ledd/2/" id="kapittel-3-ledd-2">For ferrolegeringsindustrien (Statistisk Sentralbyrås næringsgruppe 37102) er avgiftssatsen 2,6 øre pr. kWh. For den øvrige kraftkrevende industri og treforedlingsindustrien er avgiftssatsen 3,1 øre pr. kWh.</article></section><section class="section" data-name="kapIV" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/" id="kapittel-4" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/KAPITTEL_4" data-partID="k4"><h2 data-text-align="center">IV.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-ledd-1">Avgift på kullsyrefrie, alkoholfrie drikkevarer m.m.</article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§1" data-name="§1" data-partID="§1" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-1"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 1</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-1-ledd-1">Fra 1. august 1987 skal det i henhold til lov av 19. mai 1933 nr. 11 betales avgift til statskassen av alkoholfrie, kullsyrefrie drikkevarer m.m. med kr. 0,75 pr. liter salgsvare.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§2" data-name="§2" data-partID="§2" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 2</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1">Avgiftsplikten gjelder:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="a)" data-name="a)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">a)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Nektar, sirup og saft av sitrusfrukter samt konsentrat av disse.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="b)" data-name="b)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">b)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Limonade, leskedrikk, saftdrikk (herunder alkoholfri vin) o.l. konsumferdige varer.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="c)" data-name="c)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">c)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Squash. Konsentrert leskedrikk.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="d)" data-name="d)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/4/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">d)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">Blanding av avgiftsfrie og avgiftspliktige varer.</article></article></li></ul></article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§3" data-name="§3" data-partID="§3" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 3</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1">Unntatt for avgiftsplikt er:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="a)" data-name="a)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">a)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Melk, melkeprodukter.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="b)" data-name="b)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">b)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Drikkevarer fremstilt av</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/2/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-2">– kaffe o.l.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/3/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-3">– te o.l.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/4/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-4">– kakao, sjokolade</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/5/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-5">– grønnsaker</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/6/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-6">– konsentrater av ovennevnte varer.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="c)" data-name="c)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">c)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Varer i pulverform.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="d)" data-name="d)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/4/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">d)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">Essenser, ekstrakter som ikke er ment – og som departementet ikke finner tjenlig – til fremstilling av leskedrikk.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="e)" data-name="e)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/5/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">e)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/3/ledd/1/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-3-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">Vann uten tilsetting av smaksstoffer.</article></article></li></ul></article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§4" data-name="§4" data-partID="§4" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 4</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1">På vilkår som departementet kan fastsette, fritas, refunderes eller ytes forskudd for avgift på varer som:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="a)" data-name="a)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">a)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Selges til eller innføres av utenlandske, diplomatiske og konsulære tjenestemenn som nyter personlig tollfrihet.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="b)" data-name="b)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">b)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Fra tilvirkers eller importørs lager<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">1.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">utføres til utlandet</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">2.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">leveres til bruk om bord i skip eller fly i utenriks fart</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">3.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">leveres til bruk i havområder utenfor norsk territorialgrense i forbindelse med utforskning og utnytting av undersjøiske naturforekomster.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="4." data-name="4."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/4/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">4.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">legges inn på transitt-/frilager.</article></article></li></ul></article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="c)" data-name="c)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">c)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/4/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-4-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">nyttes til ervervsmessig fremstilling av annet enn drikke.</article></article></li></ul></article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§5" data-name="§5" data-partID="§5" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/5/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-5"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 5</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/5/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-5-ledd-1">Finansdepartementet fastsetter i forskrifter bestemmelser om hvilken ervervsmessig fremstilling av varer som faller inn under § 4 punkt C.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§6" data-name="§6" data-partID="§6" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/6/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-6"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 6</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/6/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-6-ledd-1">Departementet fastsetter nærmere bestemmelser om grunnlaget for avgiften og om avrunding av avgiftsbeløpene.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§7" data-name="§7" data-partID="§7" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/7/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-7"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 7</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/7/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-7-ledd-1">Oppstår det tvil om omfanget av avgiftsplikten avgjøres spørsmålet av departementet.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§8" data-name="§8" data-partID="§8" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/8/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-8"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 8</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/8/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-8-ledd-1">Departementet kan frita for eller sette ned avgiften når det oppstår enkelttilfeller eller situasjoner som ikke var overveiet da avgiftsvedtaket ble truffet og når avgiften i det spesielle enkelttilfelle får en utilsiktet virkning.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§9" data-name="§9" data-partID="§9" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/9/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-9"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 9</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/9/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-9-ledd-1">Departementet kan i forskrift gi regler om avgrensing og utfylling av bestemmelsene i §§ 1, 2, 3 og 4.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1987-06-12-502/§10" data-name="§10" data-partID="§10" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/10/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-10"><h3 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 10</span>.</h3><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/4/paragraf/10/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-4-paragraf-10-ledd-1">Departementet kan gi forskrift om at skyldig avgiftsbeløp og tilgodebeløp, som er lavere enn en nærmere bestemt fastsatt grense, ikke skal betales eller tilbakebetales.</article></article></section></main></body></html>